# Works with VS Code REST Client and JetBrains HTTP Client.

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:5678

### Health: liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

### Health: readiness, checks PostgreSQL connection
GET {{baseUrl}}/readyz

### Create user, run this before list/search examples
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ada Lovelace",
  "email": "ada-{{$timestamp}}@example.com"
}

### List users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users

### Search users with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?search=ada&limit=10&offset=0

### User stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/stats
